<p>
  <span class="nym">Rigo</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">A diminutive of any of <span class="lang">Italian</span> names ending in <i>-rigo</i>, such as <i>Rodrigo</i> (cf. <a class="nym" href="Roderick">Roderick</a>), <i>Federigo</i> (cf. <a class="nym" href="Frederick">Frederick</a>), <i>Arrigo</i> (cf. <a class="nym" href="Henry">Henry</a>).
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


